            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Nope. This is my shop! I sell the things I get while I'm traveling or doing other jobs."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I see. Whoaaa... You've got a lot of things that...I don't even know what they are."
