            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I see. Well, having a shop at the bazaar seems like it'd be pretty fun..."
